Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inside of the heart is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stars and snow are all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The big event is Valentine's!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both love and the case draw closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By Sonoko's invitation, we went to a lodge in the mountains called the "Suito House" to make Valentine chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, a reporter by the name of Nigaki Yoshitaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,went into the forest to find a certain species of wolf, but still hadn't returned when a fierce snow storm began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worried, we searched the forest for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, by the time we found him, Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining blood that wasn't wiped off,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the repositioned sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the culprit go through all the trouble of bringing Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate from the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:48.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Truth Behind Valentine's\N(Deduction Part)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Truth Behind Valentine's,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction Part!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the police say they're coming right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:00.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yuasa Chiyoko (61)\NLodge Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't an avalanche, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, an avalanche came down around 8:00 PM, and the tunnel's full of snow right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not sure when they can get here... It might be as late as tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? It's just like I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like we thought, only Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd find something on Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s camera and video camera, so I brought them back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the tape in the video camera is blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only lead we have is this single roll of film in the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we can't get it developed unless the officers are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? If we just need to develop and print the film, I can do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:04:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said he wanted to see the picture of the wolf as soon as possible, so I brought the equipment with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait a little while... I'm going to use the bathroom as a make-shift dark room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that really all you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything else in the in the victim's bag, like more rolls of film or extra tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are, but they're all unused as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is it possible he was killed before he started filming?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be that Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} likes to take pictures more than video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between the two, he actually liked filming video more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even filmed a lot last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, can we see those video tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there are a lot of them in his bag, so I don't know which ones were from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, you really shouldn't watch them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a dead person's videos, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Is there anything we shouldn't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, nothing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just kind of weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, do you want to watch them together on the TV in the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea, having more eyes might help us find some kind of lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go bring the tapes from his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is this it? The "chocolate of love" you're making for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Too bad, this one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... Don't tell me it's for another guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it... Watching someone else's home videos is really boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:57.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll make one for you when the girls get here tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:02.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What the heck? Unlike you, I prepared my present ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, you piece of junk TV, work right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for having a really old TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband treasured it because it was the first gift he gave to Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was my husband's ex-wife, but she died of an illness about 12 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saburo! Isn't it time for you to go back into your cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, she's his second wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard about it from the previous owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was mourning the loss of his wife, that old lady stayed here as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They comforted each other, and later decided to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old lady's also very good at making sweets, which has brought a lot more customers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I guess I still feel sorry for her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've heard about this? Have you stayed at this lodge before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, we were here once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from that, is this fourth video tape the last one, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the last tape that was recorded yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:28.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Now then, the tape's almost full.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither of you were on these videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! I just got here this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I got here just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, we didn't get anything useful from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I know Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture was taken right after Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see the shadow spots in the picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the pictures have them except for this last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? It's the shadow of blood on the camera lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably pressed the shutter button accidentally from the shock of being hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we don't know if those shadows are blood or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we just tried to take more pictures with that camera, and the same shadow spots were shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this confirms that he was killed in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something about Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s explanation that doesn't match up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:09:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal must be one of you three who weren't in the lodge with us during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what about the chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was left in this lodge until 8:00 PM, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, tell me who brought it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what kind of idiot would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walking all the through a snow storm, giving chocolate to a person they just killed, and then returning here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really is someone or something living in these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I ran into you guys, I saw a very suspicious person in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a tall, well-built man wearing a black wool hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shot him by mistake, thinking he was a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A black wool hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man wearing a black wool hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that it's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what the man you met in the woods looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be someone we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could tell he was a man from his muscular build,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he had sun glasses and a scarf covering his face, so I couldn't see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be Nattsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Nattsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go welcome him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't! There's still a snow storm outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Nattsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s waiting for me in the woods. Nattsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nattsuya's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died in an avalanche four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm really sorry, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Who's Nattsuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's my brother, the one who disappeared four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mika was his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the chocolate with the checkered pattern that Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made this afternoon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was going to offer them to my brother at his grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother really liked chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother's grave is also in these woods, next to the graves of the previous owner and his ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that way three years ago, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be a grave for each person who died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, wild animals destroyed most of them, and now only those three graves remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come those three graves were the only ones that didn't get destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably because I take Saburo to visit them everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband used to always take him there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway... Unless there's someone else besides us hiding somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal must be that suspicious man in the woods who was wearing a wool hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know when that Nigaki guy was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we know the criminal's the one who put the chocolate on his lap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You left the chocolate here around 8:00 PM while looking for Nigaki, and stayed together until you found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's impossible for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran into you not far from the lodge, so you probably just started searching for Nigaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it takes at least 20 minutes to go from the lodge to the crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have enough time to get the chocolate and put it on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's also impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because at 8:00 PM, I was far away from the lodge, watching the avalanche cover up the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you could have just heard about the avalanche from the news on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I called the police after we returned to the lodge, they had just received the report about the avalanche.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since that girl made the chocolate, wouldn't she have had the best opportunity to put it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took your friend and left before everyone else had gone to start searching, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it also true that you weren't together the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. We split up in the middle of searching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could have prepared a similar chocolate in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and placed that one on Nigaki when you "searched for him" the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you snuck back here while everyone else was looking for him and hid the chocolate you made today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to make everyone believe that the criminal stole your chocolate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of-Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was already snowing when we first went searching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was killed when you said, it would be snowing in this picture, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you want to compare them yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took pictures of all the chocolates we made today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look at them closely, the one found at the crime scene has melted a little bit, and has a small mark on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the handwriting and shape is exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's someone who can make an exact copy like this, I'd love to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, your deduction is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least we can rest easy now, knowing that the culprit isn't one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, good night, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the criminal really is the man wearing the black wool hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, were the pictures on the film in Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}' camera really taken in the past two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the film was full, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he have put a new roll of film inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't we compare those photos to the still frames of the video he recorded yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The outfits in the photos and video are exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was taking the pictures and video, so he wasn't able to be compared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look through the window in the first photo, you can also see that they were both taken last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the last picture with the blood spots on it must have been taken this afternoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one left the lodge since our arrival yesterday, until he went to take photos in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that means no one could have taken the picture except him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a possibility that the photo was tampered with while it was being developed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was standing right next to me while I was developing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... She didn't do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even wore gloves when she removed the film from the camera, so she wouldn't get her fingerprints on the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, wouldn't it be easy to know if the photo was edited just by checking the negatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! There was those strange, completely black photos, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Completely black photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were some pictures before the last picture with the blood spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the pictures were so dark, we couldn't see anything on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we thought that something might have been covering the lens when the shutter was pressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick was the blood spots on the photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I still don't know how the criminal shot that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the point I don't understand the most is the chocolate placed on the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having it there ruins all of my possible explanations behind the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Saburo! It's your favorite ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the man wearing the black wool hat really is the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When I came here last year, you loved playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why did you name your dog Saburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taro used to have a another dog named Jiro, but he's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? He died?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. My husband, Taro, used to have a dog named Jiro, another hunting dog like Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:19.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Taro means "First Son", Jiro means "Second Son," and Saburo means "Third Son."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me when that Jiro died only a little while after Reiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to see a picture of Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think there are some in my husband's photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's kept in the room that Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go and get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, does Saburo have any strange habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like going out for walks on his own, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he just stays in the lodge most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time he usually leaves the house is when we go visit the graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a very smart dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we get close to the graves, he runs ahead, sits there, and waits for me happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, he does have one unusual habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't eat anything on a stormy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be because he's sad that he can't go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the day after the snow storm's over, he eats a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those guys were rooting around looking through everyone's stuff without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought we might find something that would give us some kind of lead for the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-We didn't take anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose you won't mind if I search you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go to the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a streak of blood on this sweatshirt, but it looks like the middle part is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the sweatshirt Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was wearing when he cut himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He cut himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was chopping the chocolate into pieces, he accidentally cut his left thumb with the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cut wasn't very big, but since he was afraid of blood, he swung his hand around and got it on his sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, Granny was shocked and hurried to get the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako was so worried about him, she started crying in his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I had to try to calm him down instead, to keep things from getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Ako was probably the most tired person there, since she had to take care of him afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? The dog on the left is Jiro, and the one on the right is Saburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The medals on their necks are awards the local government gave them because they had helped save several people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait. It might have Saburo on the left and Jiro on the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand everything about this case now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know why there are two completely black photos before the blood-spotted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who brought the chocolate, and why it was placed on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most importantly, I know who killed Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that man wearing the black wool hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, Uncle Kogoro's going to explain it to everyone in the kitchen right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the culprit can only be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.45,0:24:17.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Truth Behind Valentine's\N(Solution Part)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: The Truth Behind Valentine's (Solution Part).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Completely black photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:24.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll finally find the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Whenever something's solved, that person is never around, right?
